1-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… and Kyriake.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":277,"html":280},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>... e Kyriake.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":282,"html":283},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The fragment is probably part of a Christian epitaph: \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Κυριακή\u003C/span> must have been the name of the deceased (perhaps not the only one mentioned in the epitaph if \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κ\u003C/span> is an abbreviation for \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">καί\u003C/span> as in IMusCatania 167 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001648\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001648\u003C/a>) and not the indication of the day of Sunday (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κυριακὴ [ἡμήρα]\u003C/span>), as Ferrua believed. This is the only occurrence of this name in Catania, whereas it is more widespread in Christian inscriptions from Syracuse (see LGPN 3A: 262).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":285,"html":286},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Libertini 1931 43 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini NSA 1931 370 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1938 70 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1981 93 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1981 113 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1989 110 no.420 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 180 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":288,"html":289},"handnote","\u003Cp>Irregular letters, A with serifs and straight bar.\u003C/p> Lines 1-2  37-42  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":291,"html":292},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[294,296,299,300],{"html":295},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou",{"id":297,"lang":126,"html":298},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-text=\"καὶ\">κ(αὶ?)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">Κυριακή\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":295},{"id":301,"lang":126,"html":302},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003C